::FZ/Shredder/Prowl::

FZ holds back his laugh at the crow's comment and starts shooting at him.

~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

Shredder dodges and growls as the shots dig into his right shoulder. He lifts both of his guns, firing at BrightBlade.

~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

Prowl lands near Iron Raptor. Seeing the battle on the Ark's scanners, he had flown here. He looks down at her laying on the ground.

"Striker and I will come back for you two later." He says to Plintissa and Suukie as he grabs Iron Raptor and flies off.
